 LINK Options 

  /A   Set .EXE Alignment           /NOI   Preserve Case Sensitivity
  /B   Run in Batch Mode            /NOL   No Copyright Message
  /CO  Prepare for Debugging        /NON   Order Segments w/o NULLs
  /CP  Set Max Allocation Space     /NOP   Disable Code-Segment Packing
  /DO  Order Segments               /O     Set Overlay Interrupt
  /DS  Control Data Loading         /PACKC Pack Code
  /E   Pack Executable Files        /PACKD Pack Data
  /F   Optimize Far Calls           /PADC  Pad Code Segments
  /HE  Display Help                 /PADD  Pad Data Segments
  /HI  Load High                    /PAU   Pause During Linking
  /INC Prepare for ILINK            /PM    Name Application Type
  /INF Display Process Info         /Q     Specify Quick Library
  /LI  Include Line Numbers         /SE    Set Max Number of Segments
  /M   List Public Symbols          /ST    Control Stack Size
  /NOD Ignore Default Libraries     /T     Generate .COM File
  /NOE Ignore Extended Dictionary   /W     Issue Fixup Warning
  /NOF No Far-Call Optimization     /?     Short Help
  /NOG No Group Association

